* **Response Time:** Significantly reduced reaction time compared to manual administration.

## Results and Impact

The AI-Driven Autonomous and Adaptive Firewall significantly enhances network security by shifting from reactive to proactive defense. The system successfully demonstrates the ability to detect complex intrusion patterns, including SQL injections and DDoS attacks, with high accuracy. By automating the mitigation process through Reinforcement Learning and SDN, the system minimizes human dependency, reduces false positives, and ensures a self-healing security infrastructure capable of withstanding modern cyber threats.

